    "method_notes": [
      "Nuisances (alpha,beta,ln sigma_int) are NOT exactly linear-Gaussian (they enter the per-SN variance), so exact analytic marginalisation is unavailable; used profile + Laplace (3x3 finite-difference Hessian of the M-marginalised -2lnL at each grid point).",
