      "Nuisance prior volumes for (alpha,beta,sigma_int,M) are identical for both models and are omitted; they cancel exactly in lnB.",
      "Expected Laplace accuracy: with N=1580 the conditional likelihood in (alpha,beta,ln sig) is very nearly Gaussian; the residual error largely cancels between models (same nuisance structure). See lnB_profile_only_variant for the size of the whole Laplace det term."
